## 3. Utils
All reusable logic lives in /utils/. Organized by domain:

  /utils/cn.ts         → className merge helper (clsx + tailwind-merge)
  /utils/date.ts       → date formatting and parsing
  /utils/string.ts     → string manipulation
  /utils/number.ts     → number formatting
  /utils/api.ts        → API helpers and error handling
  /utils/validation.ts → form and data validation

Never duplicate logic across files. If it is used more than once, it
belongs in /utils/. Always import from /utils/ — never redefine locally.

